Each of these cards will give you ideas about what can help you be at your best and stay on track even if times are tough.

 Everyone is different. Use the space on the back to write or draw things that are helpful for you.

 My Wellbeing Kit is a project of the Clarence Community Health and Wellbeing Advisory Committee health Promotion Working Group.
 It was developed with people from Flourish. DHHS Public Health Service, THS Mental Health Services, Partners in Recovery
 [Colony 47], Youth Assist, and the Mental Health Council of Tasmania.

 Illustrations by Shiloh Longbottom.
